<a href="https://iono.fm/e/645010">Content hosted by iono.fm</a> Top 5 Chivas Venture finalist and founder of Blue Avocado Investments Kelvin Bester explains how his Terra-Nebula+O2 system works – manipulating the root systems of plants and increasing their internal pressure, creating favourable conditions for trees to survive and flourish. The Chivas Venture competition gives away $1 million in no-strings funding, as well as expert coaching at the Chivas Venture Accelerator Programme, to social entrepreneurs who blend profit with purpose. The winner of the SA leg will be announced on January 23. Brought to you by Chivas Venture.